Abstract = {{In this paper a new approach is presented to increase the time-step size
   for an explicit discontinuous Galerkin numerical method. The attributes
   Of this approach are demonstrated on standard tests for the
   shallow-water equations on the sphere. The addition of multiwavelets to
   the discontinuous Galerkin method, which has the benefit of being
   scalable, flexible, and conservative, provides a hierarchical scale
