   algorithms and the application of heuristics designed to insure the
   quality of the coarse grids, and shown results from a prototype serial
   version of the algorithm.
   In this paper we describe an implementation of a parallel ANIG code,
   using the algorithm of A.J. Cleary, R.D. Falgout, V.E. Henson, J.E.
