Abstract = {{We present a convergent high-order accurate scheme for the solution of
   linear conservation laws in geometrically complex domains. As our main
   example we include a detailed development and analysis of a scheme for
   the time-domain solution of Maxwell's equations in a three-dimensional
   domain. The fully unstructured spatial discretization is made possible
