Abstract = {{We test the behaviour of a unified continuous/discontinuous Galerkin
   (CG/DG) shallow-water model in spherical geometry with curved elements
   on three different grids of ubiquitous use in atmospheric modelling: (i)
   the cubed-sphere, (ii) the reduced latitude-longitude, and (iii) the
